node.title: 82 Percent of Americans Say Regular Items Costing More Than Usual as Inflation Soars
node.description: Sixty-four percent of respondents in the CBS News/YouGov poll said items are often not in stock, and 55 percent noted that deliveries are taking longer than usual.
